AuthenticationToken.description: Amazon WorkDocs authentication token. This field should not be set when using administrative API actions, as in accessing the API using AWS credentials.

ContentCreatedTimestamp.description: The time stamp when the content of the document was originally created.

ContentModifiedTimestamp.description: The time stamp when the content of the document was modified.

ContentType.description: The content type of the document.

DocumentSizeInBytes.description: The size of the document, in bytes.

ParentFolderId.description: The ID of the parent folder.
